 ## Description
Improves text readability on mobile devices by increasing line heights.

## Problem
- Line heights too tight on small screens (harder to read)
- Text feels cramped on mobile viewports
- Poor reading experience for longer content

## Solution
- Increase body line-height to 1.6 on mobile
- Set heading line-height to 1.3 for better hierarchy
- Apply same spacing to paragraphs and lists

## Impact
- Better readability on phones
- Less eye strain for users
- Improved mobile content experience
- WCAG 2.1 compliant text spacing

## Testing
- Test on iPhone SE (smallest screen)
- Verify text doesn't overlap
- Check all pages for readability
